      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "你有没有发现，蝴蝶的左边和右边长得一模一样？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "symmetry",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/symmetry/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.61,
      "size": 25776,
      "text": "这种左右一样的美，数学上叫做对称。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "symmetry",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/symmetry/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.72,
      "size": 27504,
      "text": "今天我们一起来看看，对称到底藏着怎样的规律。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "symmetry",
      "section_id": "mirror",
      "line_id": "mirror-1",
      "filename": "mirror-mirror-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/symmetry/yunxi/mirror-mirror-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "想象在图案中间竖一面镜子，左边照出来正好是右边。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "symmetry",
      "section_id": "mirror",
      "line_id": "mirror-2",
      "filename": "mirror-mirror-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/symmetry/yunxi/mirror-mirror-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.44,
      "size": 23040,
      "text": "这条镜子所在的线，就叫对称轴。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "symmetry",
      "section_id": "mirror",
      "line_id": "mirror-3",
      "filename": "mirror-mirror-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/symmetry/yunxi/mirror-mirror-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "蝴蝶、人脸、树叶，都有这样一条对称轴。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "symmetry",
      "section_id": "rotation",
      "line_id": "rotation-1",
      "filename": "rotation-rotation-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/symmetry/yunxi/rotation-rotation-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.51,
      "size": 24192,
      "text": "还有一种对称，是把图案绕着中心转一转。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "symmetry",
      "section_id": "rotation",
      "line_id": "rotation-2",
      "filename": "rotation-rotation-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/symmetry/yunxi/rotation-rotation-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.34,
      "size": 37440,
      "text": "风车转四分之一圈，看起来和原来一样，这叫四重旋转对称。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "symmetry",
      "section_id": "rotation",
      "line_id": "rotation-3",
      "filename": "rotation-rotation-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/symmetry/yunxi/rotation-rotation-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "海星转五分之一圈重合，雪花转六分之一圈重合。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "symmetry",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/symmetry/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "切换不同的图案，数一数它转几次才能回到原样。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "symmetry",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/symmetry/yunxi/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "再找一找，哪些图案还能沿着对称轴翻折重合。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "symmetry",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/symmetry/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.48,
      "size": 23616,
      "text": "对称就是变换之后还能和自己重合。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "symmetry",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
